### Quick Confirm + Batch t.co Unwrapper (Free, No API)

**Yes, exactly**: TweetDeck lists → Alert hits → Screenshot/log bursts (handle/text/t.co/media/time) for 30min → Dump in Google Sheet (cols: Handle | Timestamp | Full Text | t.co Link | Media URL). Sort by time/text for clusters. Double-space tic? Regex search `\.  ` in sheet—flags copy-paste ops.

#### Fastest Free Way: Browser Console Script (20 Links = 30sec, 100% Free)
No extensions, no API keys, no cash. Works on X.com search/tweet pages. Extracts **all t.co** from page + auto-resolves to final URL (e.g., bit.ly → rawstory.com).

**Steps**:
1. **Collect t.co Links**:
   - X Advanced Search: `"your phrase" within_time:30m min_faves:10` (your story window).
   - Scroll to load 20+ tweets → Right-click page → Inspect → Console tab.

2. **Paste & Run This Script** (copy exactly):
   ```javascript
   // Extract all t.co from page + resolve redirects
   let tweets = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-testid="tweet"]'));
   let results = [];
   tweets.forEach((tweet, i) => {
     let handle = tweet.querySelector('[data-testid="User-Name"]')?.textContent?.trim() || 'N/A';
     let text = tweet.querySelector('[data-testid="tweetText"]')?.textContent?.trim() || '';
     let link = Array.from(tweet.querySelectorAll('a[href^="https://t.co/"]')).pop()?.href || 'No Link';
     if (link) {
       fetch(link, {redirect: 'follow'}).then(r => r.url).then(finalUrl => {
         results.push({handle, text: text.slice(0,100)+'...', tco: link, final: finalUrl});
         console.table(results);  // Live table updates!
       });
     }
   });
   ```
   - Hit Enter → Watch **Console table** populate: Handle | Text Snippet | t.co | **final URL** (e.g., same bit.ly 15/20x = bingo!).
   - Copy table → Paste Sheet. Handles 50+ tweets instantly.

3. **If No Search Page**: 
   - TweetDeck: Export list view as CSV (handles/text), grab t.co manually (5sec each).
   - Single tweet: Open → F12 > Network > Click link → See "response URL" chain (bit.ly there).

**Fallbacks (Even Faster for 20)**:
| Method | Time | How |
|--------|------|-----|
| **Unshorten.it** | 20sec | Paste t.co one-by-one (Enter → instant). No login. |
| **CheckShortURL.com** | 15sec | Same, bulk-feels (tab between). |
| **Curl Loop (Terminal/Replit.com)** | 10sec | Free Replit: `for url in $(cat links.txt); do curl -L -s -w "%{url_effective}\n" $url; done` |
| **Sheets Hack** | 1min | Col A: t.co list → Col B: `=HYPERLINK(A1)` → Click each (browser follows redirect, copy address bar). |

**Pro Tip**: Final URLs cluster? WHOIS(bit.ly domain via whois.com) → Owner/email = operator lead. Same bit.ly batch-upload timestamp? Def coordinated.

Test on last week's mayor story: Search `"mayor [phrase]"` + double space → Script it. Hit me with sample t.co for demo. 🚀
